  25 Feb 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> -mozc-ut-2.16.2014.102.20150114.ebuild:
  Drop old version 2.16.2014.102.20150114.

          deleted:    mozc-ut-2.16.2014.102.20150114.ebuild

  25 Feb 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> metadata.xml,
  mozc-ut-2.16.2061.102.20150214.ebuild:
  fix ver 2.16.2068.102.20150214 to avoid segfault.

   Finally, mozc-ut-2.16.2068.102.20150214.ebuild still use gcc instead of
  clang
  (though official Mozc has become to use clang).

   Building Mozc with clang, built binaries fall in segmentation fault.
  Probably it is specific problem on Gentoo systems.
  GCC is recommended.

*mozc-ut-2.16.2061.102.20150214 (17 Feb 2015)

  17 Feb 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +mozc-ut-2.16.2061.102.20150214.ebuild:
  add ver 2.16.2061.102.20150214.

  - Protobuf
    Mozc's protobuf dependency was reverted from ver 2.6.1 to r512.
   See Mozc r482; https://code.google.com/p/mozc/source/detail?r=482
   Therefore this ebuild file calls protobuf ver 2.5.0.

   - Clang
    Mozc became to depend on Clang.
   See Mozc r506; https://code.google.com/p/mozc/source/detail?r=506

   - Removed "build_mozc.py build_tools"
    "build_mozc.py build_tools" was removed.
   See Mozc r507; https://code.google.com/p/mozc/source/detail?r=507

          new file:mozc-ut-2.16.2061.102.20150214.ebuild

  10 Feb 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> metadata.xml,
  mozc-ut-2.16.2014.102.20150114.ebuild:
  Omit deprecated python.eclass. Add correct licenses.

  - Updated to use python-single-r1.eclass
           python.eclass is deprecated.
           We should call python-r1(*).eclass instead of python.eclass.

  - Fixed licenses
           Japanese WordNet(EJDIC) has a derivative license of
  "Princeton"(WordNet).
           The licenses of "Hatena Keywords" and "Nico Nico Pedia" is not
  clear,
          so *they can be "all-rights-reserved"* .
          Please edit your /etc/portage/package.license to install.
           See http://www.geocities.jp/ep3797/mozc_01.html

  - Fixed metadata.xml
           For the Quality Assurance.

          modified:   metadata.xml
          modified:   mozc-ut-2.16.2014.102.20150114.ebuild
          new file:   /licenses/wn-ja
          new file:   /profiles/license_groups

  07 Feb 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> mozc-ut-2.16.2014.102.20150114.ebuild:
  Remove protobuf dependency.

